放异彩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-10/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 11:12:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>芬兰表示，芬兰和中国国家主席讨论了管道损坏问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/finnish-chinese-presidents-discussed-pipeline-damage-finland-says-2024-01-10/</link><description>芬兰总统绍利·尼尼斯托周三表示，他与中国国家主席习近平就去年连接芬兰和爱沙尼亚的波罗的海天然气管道遭受的损害进行了建设性会谈。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 10:39:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/finnish-chinese-presidents-discussed-pipeline-damage-finland-says-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>行业协会：大众、丰田2023年中国市场份额萎缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-toyota-saw-china-market-share-shrink-2023-industry-association-2024-01-10/</link><description>周三的行业数据显示，随着传统国际汽车制造商将市场份额拱手让给中国竞争对手，大众集团和丰田汽车去年在全球最大汽车市场的份额出现萎缩。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 10:12:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-toyota-saw-china-market-share-shrink-2023-industry-association-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年达沃斯：极端天气和错误信息是全球最大风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/davos-2024-extreme-weather-misinformation-top-global-risks-2024-01-10/</link><description>世界经济论坛（WEF）周三发布的一项调查显示，风险专家认为极端天气和错误信息最有可能在未来几年引发全球危机。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 09:42:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/davos-2024-extreme-weather-misinformation-top-global-risks-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>印度莫迪在商业峰会上吸引投资者，企业公布巨额支出计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-pitches-growth-resilience-woo-investors-2024-01-10/</link><description>印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪周三在其家乡举行的一次大型商业峰会上宣扬了印度的经济前景，马鲁蒂铃木公司和阿达尼公司公布了总价值近 300 亿美元的投资计划。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 08:00:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-pitches-growth-resilience-woo-investors-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>充满选举的 2024 年将如何影响世界市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-election-2024-01-10/</link><description>市场面临“投票箱重磅炸弹”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 07:29:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-election-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国的政策困境：信贷提振是否会导致通货紧缩？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-policy-dilemma-is-boosting-credit-deflationary-2024-01-10/</link><description>中国央行在消除通货紧缩威胁方面面临着一个重大障碍：更多的信贷流向生产力而非消费，暴露了经济的结构性缺陷并降低了货币政策工具的有效性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 06:05:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-policy-dilemma-is-boosting-credit-deflationary-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>红海袭击：零售商急于避免春季系列产品延误</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/retailers-rush-avoid-delays-spring-collections-due-red-sea-attacks-2024-01-10/</link><description>高管和专家告诉路透社，世界各地的零售商都在中国农历新年假期前备货，并寻求通过红海运输的航空或铁路替代方案，以避免今年春天货架空空。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 06:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/retailers-rush-avoid-delays-spring-collections-due-red-sea-attacks-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>习近平向艾奥瓦州老朋友表示世界需要中美关系稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/old-friend-iowa-xi-says-world-requires-stability-china-us-ties-2024-01-10/</link><description>据中国官方媒体周三报道，中国国家主席习近平最近在回信一位爱荷华州人的来信中表示，世界的未来需要中美关系的稳定。他与爱荷华州人在近四十年前首次会面。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 05:57:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/old-friend-iowa-xi-says-world-requires-stability-china-us-ties-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>民意调查 随着全球贸易回暖，中国12月出口有所改善</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-seen-improving-december-global-trade-picks-up-2024-01-10/</link><description>路透调查显示，中国出口可能在 12 月份连续第二个月增长更快，这进一步表明，由于电子行业的好转以及 2024 年借贷成本下降的预期，全球贸易开始复苏。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 05:13:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-seen-improving-december-global-trade-picks-up-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾、印度尼西亚领导人就南海和东盟集团举行会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-philippines-discuss-south-china-sea-developments-marcos-2024-01-10/</link><description>菲律宾和印度尼西亚领导人周三在马尼拉会面，讨论南海的事态发展以及东南亚国家之间建立更紧密关系的努力等一系列问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 03:59:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-philippines-discuss-south-china-sea-developments-marcos-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>台湾选举前台湾与中国关系的关键事实</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/key-facts-taiwan-china-relations-ahead-taiwan-elections-2024-01-10/</link><description>台湾周六将举行投票选举新总统和国会。尽管台湾政府反对，中国仍将台湾视为中国的一个省及其领土的一部分，因此将密切关注这一结果。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 03:29:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/key-facts-taiwan-china-relations-ahead-taiwan-elections-2024-01-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>